# AWS can be access through the following ways:

    1. AWS Management Console (which is protected by password and MFA)
    2. AWS Command Line Interface (CLI) (protected by access keys)
    3. AWS Software Developer Kit (SDK) (for code, protected by access keys)

Access keys are generated through AWS Console

# AWS CLI

This tool enables access to AWS services through commands.
Direct access to public APIs of AWS services.

Open source : [https://github.com/aws/aws-cli]

# AWS SDK

1. APIs (language specifics)
2. Access and Manage AWS services programmatically.
3. Useful in embedding in applications ro use AWS services.

